title: Bonus Podcast: Giants Bench Eli Manning (Football 11/29)
description:
On a special edition of the Pick Six podcast, Nick Kostos, Pete Prisco and Jason La Canfora analyze the Giants decision to bench Eli Manning and start Geno Smith. The guys break down the shocking move from all angles in this bonus pod.
